title: Best of Clancy And The Rockets Week 6: Wrapping Up 2018
description:
Clancy & The Rockets finish off 2018 talking about drinking in the office, candlepin bowling, strip clubs, Game of Thrones and KFC's trip to the MGM. KFC closes out the final segment of 2018 and looks forward to 2019.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kfcr
